cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.IT

This paper deals with the benefit of sexual recombination in evolutionary computation, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the performance of different algorithms in handling noisy fitness functions, which is a topic related to statistical learning and information theory. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper uses mathematical proofs and analysis, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
